\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf2 \cb3 We live in an era where the people have been exposed to such a large number of external stimuli. The world dictates the pace, which unnecessarily we try to keep up with. This thesis poses the question, "How to find time and place for a moment of reflection, in this reality?". This project is located in Sliema; a representation of an over-stimulated environment. However, amidst its psychedelic world, today many visitors still seek a reconfiguration of one\'92s self mind by the coast as the sound of sea overtakes the nearby chaotic atmosphere. 
